{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act21side_level_act21side_05_beg","storyGroup":"act21side","storySort":11,"storyDependence":"act21side_level_act21side_st02","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"IS-5","storyName":"恒久法则","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"瓦拉赫愤怒于德克萨斯的选择，拉维妮娅提出要见贝纳尔多，准备质问他的选择。\n","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act21side/level_act21side_05_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act21side_05","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":9,"next":11,"characters":["瓦拉赫","德克萨斯","德米特里","拉维妮娅","能天使","空","可颂","卡特琳娜","乔万娜"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_bg_33_g7_reception.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"dialog","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":10},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":11},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":12},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"虽然我也考虑过莱昂图索在诓我的可能性，但是，一见到你我就知道了。","id":14,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你是货真价实的德克萨斯。","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"......","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"容我自我介绍一下，我是罗塞蒂家族的瓦拉赫。","id":19,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"你是哥伦比亚人？","id":21,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"当然，罗塞蒂家族的大部分成员都是哥伦比亚人。","id":23,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"如何，这里的监狱生活？","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"没什么特别的。","id":27,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"真奇怪，照理说，你不应该在监狱里待这么久，贝洛内到底是怎么想的。","id":29,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"遵纪守法，很奇怪吗？","id":31,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"遵纪守法？但是叙拉古的法院，跟所谓的法律真的有关系吗？","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"比如，在大部分的叙拉古城市，一个家族成员的成年礼，就是上一次法庭，进一次监狱。","id":34,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"然后，他的家族成员会像迎接一名战士一样，将他带回家族。","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"这个国家表面上的一切，对我们这种身处地下秩序的人来说，都形同虚设。","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"所以呢？","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你是在哥伦比亚长大的人，难道还需要我来解释吗？","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"“可笑”，我没有除此以外的评价。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"当然，也拜此所赐，我们才能够如此顺利地在这里扎根。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"你很喜欢和人聊政治吗？","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"看来你不喜欢。","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"其实我也不喜欢。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"我就直说吧，你为什么没有死？","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"与你无关。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"好吧，那我换个问法，你为什么要回来？","id":53,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"莱昂图索没有告诉你吗？我欠贝洛内一次。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"那么，我是不是可以理解为，你知道贝洛内是为了让你对付我们罗塞蒂才让你回来的，你还是回来了。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"我也是回来之后才知道的，不过——你确实可以这么理解。","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你的坦诚甚至让我怀疑是不是我出了问题，最后的德克萨斯。","id":61,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"难道你要告诉我，你已经完全忘记了，德克萨斯这个姓氏曾经统领着哥伦比亚大大小小的家族？","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你的爷爷，萨尔瓦多雷曾经是每一个哥伦比亚家族成员的信仰？！","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"......","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"德克萨斯留下的一切，都与我无关。","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"都与你无关？！","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":70},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":71},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_smashtable","volume":"1","id":72},{"type":"playsound","key":"$blooddrop","volume":"1","id":73},{"type":"text","text":"瓦拉赫一拳打在旁边的茶几上，鲜血从手指上流了下来。","id":74},{"type":"text","text":"而他仿佛浑然未觉。","id":75},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你是切利尼娜·德克萨斯！萨尔瓦多雷的孙女！","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你只要活着，那些东西就与你有关！","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"光是你的名字出现在罗塞蒂的会议桌上，就会让我们不得不去改变行动的方针！","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"我们曾经以德克萨斯为荣！","id":81,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"为了不让萨尔瓦多雷的心血白费，你知不知道，乔万娜花了多少力气才将剩下的哥伦比亚家族重新统合起来？","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你知不知道，我们如何向西西里夫人卑躬屈膝，最终选择向叙拉古回流，从哥伦比亚千里迢迢返回叙拉古？","id":84,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"为了生存，我们甚至将建造移动城市的技术和盘托出，几乎在免费为叙拉古建造新的移动城市——","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"这一切都是因为德克萨斯的陨落，我们不得不接受了这个事实。","id":86,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"而现在，你，最后的德克萨斯，堂而皇之地踏上了这片土地。","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"却说你与这一切无关，你只是来还债。","id":88,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":89},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你甚至站在了我们的对立面！","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你欠贝洛内的？","id":92,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"既然你活着，那你欠哥伦比亚家族的更多！","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"我或许欠乔万娜一个交代，但我不欠哥伦比亚家族的。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"完成和贝洛内的约定后，我会离开叙拉古。","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你觉得我会相信吗？","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你的存在，就是对罗塞蒂根基的动摇。","id":99,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"......","id":101,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"乔万娜呢？","id":103,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"什么？","id":105,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"我问，为什么是你来见我，而不是乔万娜。","id":107,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"我是她的代言人。","id":109,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"她不会说，向西西里夫人卑躬屈膝。","id":111,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"她也不会派一个使者来见我。","id":112,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你以为你了解她？","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"从你的表现来看，或许是这样。","id":116,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"......","id":118,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"啊......真可惜。","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"看来，我还是不够了解传闻中的德克萨斯。","id":121,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"我还以为我的演技不错。","id":123,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"不算差。","id":125,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"只是，你高谈阔论着叙拉古，仿佛已经看穿了这个国家的样子，让我觉得......很熟悉。","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5d/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"我不推荐你这么做。","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"为什么？","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b6/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"因为这意味着......你还不够了解这个国家。","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"......","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"不过，有一点你说得对，我既然回来了，应该和乔万娜聊一聊。","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_1028_texas2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你见不到她的。","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":139},{"type":"character","id":140},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_shufflecards","channel":"a","loop":"true","id":141},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":142},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"0","id":143},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":144},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":145},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_698_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_698_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":146},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":147},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"不好意思，最后的德克萨斯。","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你太像一个叙拉古人了，不，你是一个彻头彻尾的叙拉古人。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"所以，我不能让你见首领。","id":151,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你会动摇她，你会动摇许多人，你会毁了许多东西。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_695_1#4$1","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"所以，请回吧。","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"去履行你和贝洛内的约定吧，然后，滚回你苟且偷生的地方。","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你想做什么都是你的自由。","id":156,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"但是，唯独有一点，请你记住。","id":157,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"罗塞蒂家族，不欢迎你。","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/24/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":159},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"10","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":160},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"1","id":161},{"type":"text","text":"德克萨斯站起身，向门口走去。","id":162},{"type":"dialog","id":163},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_698_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_698_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.3","id":164},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-150","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":165},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":166},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"150","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":167},{"type":"text","text":"杀手们不自觉地为她让出一条道路。","id":168},{"type":"dialog","id":169},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":170},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":171},{"type":"text","text":"她环视一圈，从这些哥伦比亚人的眼中读出了愤怒，不解，厌恶，困惑等等情绪。","id":172},{"type":"text","text":"这就是这个姓氏带来的东西。","id":173},{"type":"text","text":"德克萨斯。","id":174},{"type":"text","text":"她叹了口气，走出房间。","id":175},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":176},{"type":"dialog","id":177},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":179},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":180},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/74/Avg_bg_33_g11_mansionhall.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":181},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":182},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":183},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_dooropen","volume":"1","id":184},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":185},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#7$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":186},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":187},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#1$1","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"稀客。","id":189,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#7$1","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"我要见贝纳尔多。","id":191,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我提醒过你很多次，不要直呼首领的名字，拉维妮娅小姐。","id":193,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#7$1","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"你知道他在哪，对吗？","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我有什么理由必须告诉你吗？","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#7$1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"如果我现在站在这里，听完你作为胜利者的嘲讽，可以让你告诉我的话，我不在乎。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#8$1","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"胜利者......","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"算了。","id":203,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"告诉你也无妨，首领已经启程去萨卢佐家族的宅邸了。","id":204,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"你见不到他的。","id":205,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"你想在这座宅子怎么闹，都是你的事。","id":206,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"但是，首领既然决定去和萨卢佐家谈，那么，我劝你不要做多余的事。","id":207,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#8$1","name2":"char_empty","id":208},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"200","fadetime":"0","block":"false","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"......","id":210,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/84/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","name2":"char_empty","id":211},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"200","fadetime":"0","block":"false","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"不用你提醒我。","id":213,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":214},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":215},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-200","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":216},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":217},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"以及，拉维妮娅小姐。","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":220},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":221},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"你怎么看待我，我并不在乎。","id":223,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"但是，我希望你不要忘记。","id":224,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"莱昂是这个家族的一员，是他偏离了家族应有的轨道在先。","id":225,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"我们是一个家族，一个家族应当齐心协力。","id":226,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/db/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"轨道？","id":228,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"何必把野心说得这么好听。","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德米特里","text":"呵。","id":231,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_690_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":232},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":233},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":234},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_690_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":235},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":236},{"type":"dialog","id":237},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":238},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":239},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":240},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_rainlight_loop","loop":"true","channel":"a","id":241},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e3/Avg_bg_33_g1_srcstreet.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":242},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_distressed_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":243,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":244},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":245},{"type":"text","text":"一滴雨滴打在眼眶，顺流而下，像是一道泪痕。","id":246},{"type":"text","text":"拉维妮娅从来没有感觉到叙拉古的雨是如此冰冷。","id":247},{"type":"text","text":"但她马上擦去了雨痕。","id":248},{"type":"text","text":"还不到时候。","id":249},{"type":"dialog","id":250},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#6$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":251},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":252},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_telephonebusy","id":253},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":254},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.6","id":255},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#6$1","name2":"char_empty","focus":"-1","id":256},{"type":"charactercutin","widgetID":"1","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","style":"cutin","fadestyle":"horiz_expand_center","fadetime":"0.5","offsetx":"200","width":"200","block":"true","id":257},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"哪位？","id":259,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#6$1","name2":"char_empty","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"......我找企鹅物流。","id":261,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#6$1","name2":"char_empty","focus":"-1","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"我就是。","id":263,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#6$1","name2":"char_empty","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"现在有空吗？","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#6$1","name2":"char_empty","focus":"-1","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"正好有一点。","id":267,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#6$1","name2":"char_empty","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"你们公司都有什么业务？","id":269,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#6$1","name2":"char_empty","focus":"-1","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"送信，送话，送货，还有......送人。","id":271,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"风雨无阻。","id":272,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#2$1","name2":"char_empty","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"正好，我有一份委托。","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ee/Avg_avg_4065_judge_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":275},{"type":"dialog","id":276},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":277},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":278},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":279},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"1","id":280},{"type":"charactercutin","widgetID":"1","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":281},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#5","id":282},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":283,"musicid":2},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9b/Avg_bg_33_g8_srcroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":284},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":285},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":286},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","id":287},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.3","id":288},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":289},{"type":"character","name":"avg_103_angel_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":290},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"啊，空，你果然在卡特琳娜小姐家。","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#5","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"这里有好多资料，而且不少剧本中都能看到卡特琳娜小姐的笔记。","id":294,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_101_sora_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"她真的很喜欢自己的职业呢。","id":295,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_101_sora_5.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":296},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":297},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#4","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"唉......","id":299,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_char_101_sora_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_201_moeshd_1#13$1","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可颂","text":"别叹气啦。","id":301,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_201_moeshd_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可颂","text":"我们都知道，你也不想把演员事业只是当做寻找德克萨斯的手段。","id":302,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/54/Avg_avg_201_moeshd_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#4","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"嗯，但是，眼下的情况，还是要以见到德克萨斯为优先呢......","id":304,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_char_101_sora_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"毕竟，连那个拉普兰德也回到了叙拉古，而且还做了那么出格的事。","id":305,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_char_101_sora_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_103_angel_1#1$1","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"其实想一想也是理所当然的事情。","id":307,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"总觉得她会出现在一切德克萨斯会出现的地方。","id":308,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#4","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"你们觉得，她是想要帮德克萨斯才那么做的吗？","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_char_101_sora_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_201_moeshd_1#9$1","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可颂","text":"虽然结果上来说，德克萨斯的嫌疑确实被洗清了，但是怎么想都很奇怪吧。","id":312,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_201_moeshd_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#4","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"嗯，我也觉得，她应该是有自己的目的。","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_char_101_sora_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_201_moeshd_1#9$1","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可颂","text":"唉，我是真的不擅长应付这个人。","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_201_moeshd_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可颂","text":"说是德克萨斯的朋友肯定谈不上，但是，如果是仇家，哪有态度这么暧昧的仇家。","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5b/Avg_avg_201_moeshd_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_201_moeshd_1#12$1","id":318},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可颂","text":"搞不清楚她到底想在德克萨斯身上找到什么。","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_avg_201_moeshd_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_103_angel_1#10$1","id":320},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"但她之前送我的千层酥还蛮好吃的欸。","id":321,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_201_moeshd_1#5$1","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可颂","text":"吃货闭嘴啦。","id":323,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_201_moeshd_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_103_angel_1#9$1","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"我以前也猜不透莫斯提马在想什么，但是等我逐渐不去想这件事后，我反而有点理解了。","id":325,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"我觉得拉普兰德也是一样的。","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"像她们这样的人，与其去猜她们到底在想什么，不如干脆地接受她们的每一句话。","id":327,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"只有相信她们的每一句话都是真的，才能看穿她们最后是不是在用真实编织一个谎言。","id":328,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#4","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"是吗......","id":330,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_char_101_sora_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_201_moeshd_1#1$1","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可颂","text":"啊，我先去买点吃的，能天使，护卫就拜托你了。","id":332,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_201_moeshd_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_103_angel_1#6$1","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"放心~","id":334,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/32/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":335},{"type":"character","name":"avg_201_moeshd_1#1$1","id":336},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":337},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":338},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.5","id":339},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":340},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","id":341},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":342},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#9$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":343},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"空，又在练台词呢？","id":345,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#5","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"啊，卡特琳娜小姐，你好呀。","id":347,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_101_sora_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"因为《德克萨斯之死》的第二幕快要正式演出了，所以我最近打算努力一点。","id":348,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_101_sora_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#10$1","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"啊，已经到了这个日子了吗，我都忘了。","id":350,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9d/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#9$1","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"能天使，吃披萨吗？","id":352,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_103_angel_1#10$1","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"我要！","id":354,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#1","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"对了，卡特琳娜小姐既然是剧本作者，到时候一定会来看吧？","id":356,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_char_101_sora_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#8$1","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"嗯——","id":358,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#9$1","id":359},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"我其实就是想来告诉你，我会暂时离开一段时间。","id":360,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#3","id":361},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"欸？","id":362,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_char_101_sora_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#1","id":363},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"你要离开很久吗？","id":364,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_char_101_sora_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#8$1","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"嗯......如果顺利的话，应该不会很久吧。","id":366,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/45/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#9$1","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"放心，不是什么大事，家里出了点状况，我这个做大姐的，要回去主持一下大局而已。","id":368,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_103_angel_1#1$1","id":369},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"当姐姐的还真是辛苦欸......","id":370,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#3$1","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"哈哈，还好啦。","id":372,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#9$1","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"只可惜，第三幕的高潮我还是没有想好。","id":374,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"唉，但愿这次回老家能找到一些灵感吧。","id":375,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#4","id":376},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"好吧......","id":377,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_char_101_sora_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#11$1","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"哎，别露出这副表情嘛，只是平时见不到了而已，第二幕的上演我应该会抽空去看的。","id":379,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a3/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#9$1","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"说不定到时候去后台找你玩哦。","id":381,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#1","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"真的？","id":383,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_char_101_sora_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#9$1","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"毕竟是好不容易交到的朋友，而且又是我自己写的剧本，我也想在近距离观赏呢。","id":385,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#1","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"嗯，那就这么说定了，你过来的话一定要联络我哦！","id":387,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_char_101_sora_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#3$1","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"没问题！","id":389,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#9$1","id":390},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡特琳娜","text":"那我先走了，拜拜。","id":391,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/01/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_101_sora_1#1","id":392},{"type":"dialogue","name":"空","text":"拜拜~","id":393,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_char_101_sora_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_103_angel_1#1$1","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"能天使","text":"再见~","id":395,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/85/Avg_avg_103_angel_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":396},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":397},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":398},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":399},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/31/Avg_bg_33_g6_newtown_street.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":400},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":401},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":402},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":403},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":404},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":405},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"首领，不用带行李吗？","id":406,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#14$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":407},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔万娜","text":"等事情处理完，我还要回这里写剧本呢，有什么好带的。","id":408,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#14$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"......好吧。","id":410,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":411},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔万娜","text":"萨卢佐和贝洛内现在是什么反应？","id":412,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"萨卢佐邀请莱昂图索少爷去赴宴，贝纳尔多这头老狼应了下来。","id":414,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"这场宴会可有意思了，现在所有人都在看着他们呢。","id":415,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"我们要做些什么反应吗？","id":416,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔万娜","text":"......","id":418,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔万娜","text":"瓦拉赫，帮我安排一场行程。","id":419,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔万娜","text":"我要去看《德克萨斯之死》第二幕的上演。","id":420,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瓦拉赫","text":"你就这么关心自己写的剧本吗？","id":422,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0e/Avg_avg_npc_695_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":423},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔万娜","text":"当然，这可是我的心血之作。","id":424,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔万娜","text":"而且，你不是问我们要做什么反应吗？","id":425,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔万娜","text":"这就是我的反应，既然贝纳尔多·贝洛内都从他的剧院里走出来了。","id":426,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_687_1#13$1","name2":"avg_npc_695_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔万娜","text":"那我，乔万娜·罗塞蒂，也该回来了。","id":428,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_687_1-13$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":429},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":430},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":431},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":432},{"type":"character","id":433},{"type":"image","id":434}],"characters":["瓦拉赫","德克萨斯","德米特里","拉维妮娅","能天使","空","可颂","卡特琳娜","乔万娜"]}